- If docx Base64: decode and download directly as [.docx](file:///c:/scripts/build/search_agent/testdata/ResumeT%20-%20%7BCompany%20name%7D%20-%20%7BPosition%20name%7D%20-%20Wang%20Cuixia%20-%20%7BGenerate%20date%7D.docx) (skip [convertMarkdownToDocx](file:///c:/scripts/build/search_agent/frontend/components/ResumeManagement.tsx#79-185))
- Helper: `isBase64Docx(content: string): boolean` — checks if string is valid base64 and starts with docx magic bytes when decoded

