## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
Currently there are no automated tests for this feature. We will manually verify using the provided testdata files.

### Manual Verification Steps

1. **Start the backend:**
   ```
   cd c:\scripts\build\search_agent\backend
   start_backend.bat
   ```

2. **Upload a .docx template:**
   - Open the app in the browser
   - Go to Profile page
   - Upload [testdata/ResumeT - {Company name} - {Position name} - Wang Cuixia - {Generate date}.docx](file:///c:/scripts/build/search_agent/testdata/ResumeT%20-%20%7BCompany%20name%7D%20-%20%7BPosition%20name%7D%20-%20Wang%20Cuixia%20-%20%7BGenerate%20date%7D.docx)
   - Verify it appears in the templates list

3. **Generate a resume using the template:**
   - Go to Dashboard, select a job
   - Choose the uploaded template from the dropdown
   - Click "Generate Resume"
   - Download the resulting [.docx](file:///c:/scripts/build/search_agent/testdata/ResumeT%20-%20%7BCompany%20name%7D%20-%20%7BPosition%20name%7D%20-%20Wang%20Cuixia%20-%20%7BGenerate%20date%7D.docx)
   - **Expected:** Format matches [testdata/Resume - AUT auto - Sales Consultant Seminar Sales Specialist - WangCuixia - 20260226.docx](file:///c:/scripts/build/search_agent/testdata/Resume%20-%20AUT%20auto%20-%20Sales%20Consultant%20Seminar%20Sales%20Specialist%20-%20WangCuixia%20-%2020260226.docx) (same fonts, tables, layout)
   - **Expected:** No markdown symbols (`#`, `**`, `*`) in the output
   - **Expected:** Output filename is `Resume - [company] - [position] - Wang Cuixia - [YYYYMMDD].docx`

4. **Test Cover Letter template:**
   - Upload [testdata/Cover LetterT - {Company name} - {Position name} - {Name of applicant} - {Generate date}.docx](file:///c:/scripts/build/search_agent/testdata/Cover%20LetterT%20-%20%7BCompany%20name%7D%20-%20%7BPosition%20name%7D%20-%20%7BName%20of%20applicant%7D%20-%20%7BGenerate%20date%7D.docx)
   - Generate a cover letter for the same job
   - **Expected:** Format matches `testdata/Cover Letter - AUT auto - ... - WangCuixia - 20260226.docx`

5. **Test Chinese template:**
   - Switch language to Chinese (中文)
   - Upload [testdata/ResumeT - {公司名称} - {职位名称} - 王翠霞 - {Generate date}.docx](file:///c:/scripts/build/search_agent/testdata/ResumeT%20-%20%7B%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%7D%20-%20%7B%E8%81%8C%E4%BD%8D%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%7D%20-%20%E7%8E%8B%E7%BF%A0%E9%9C%9E%20-%20%7BGenerate%20date%7D.docx)
   - Generate resume
   - **Expected:** Chinese content, correct output filename

6. **Test partial template (user controls sections):**
   - Create a test [.docx](file:///c:/scripts/build/search_agent/testdata/ResumeT%20-%20%7BCompany%20name%7D%20-%20%7BPosition%20name%7D%20-%20Wang%20Cuixia%20-%20%7BGenerate%20date%7D.docx) with only `{skills}` and `{summary}` tokens (no `{projects}`)
   - Generate resume
   - **Expected:** Only skills and summary sections are generated; no projects section appears
